{"tid":1251469,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【周融Blog】政治啞忍盲讓之下的 一鼓作氣再而衰三而竭？","createTime":"2019-06-22T14:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T01:32:22.000Z","uid":53369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"84c9765c84a2bb8f4dbcb784cfb9e839c52ad6ba","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭</span>！香港的反修例遊行在特區政府政治決定的啞忍盲讓路缐下，是否也逃不過這個定律？<br />\n現場觀察，星期六凌晨二時可能尚有足夠人手圍警總，但過多兩個小時，又剩下多少人呢？<br />\n更別說度過漫漫長夜後情況會如何！<span style=\"color: red;\">人少時會不會有人被捕</span>？這個可能性不得不考慮！這是現場主事者面對的難題，所以早退是唯一選擇！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十小時疲態現 入夜後人漸少 </span><br />\n按照這個入夜後人愈來愈少的趨勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">將來的示威活動會不會只能吸引足夠遊行人數，但十個八個小時後就已疲態畢露</span>？<br />\n若這是事實，幕後黑手們肯定大失所望了。<span style=\"color: red;\">一個持久力不足的運動如何能令香港亂上加亂</span>？亂不起來的香港又如何拖累到背後的中國？<br />\n最新一場衝突其實已暴露出<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者人數不足</span>的現實：由包圍政總延長戰線至警察總部尚可以，再拖長到稅務大樓已是鞭長莫及了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻一路尚可以</span> 圍政總反示弱</span><br />\n這一役大家可以看得到，反對派<span style=\"color: red;\">屯重兵來阻擋一條主龫道可以，再加龍和道，然後進佔金鐘道已經不易了</span>。<br />\n示威群眾想<span style=\"color: red;\">包圍政總，已是說易行難</span>。人手不足不是示威，反是示弱！<br />\n莫非政府這次採取的<span style=\"color: red;\">啞忍盲讓策略除了難看及令親者痛之外，實際上是神來之筆</span>？究竟是無心之得，還是學中日之戰之誘敵深入，不得而知了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港慢慢靜下 政府威信蕩然</span><br />\n示威群眾群龍無首之局，究竟是主事者防避佔中主角被捕的命運，還是民眾出乎意料的自發衝動？也是另一個不得而知了。<br />\n看到一些反對派老領導在示威人群中的遭遇，看來是後者也不足為奇。<br />\n假使如此，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港打後只要沒有什麼刺激下，可能會慢慢地靜下來了</span>。<br />\n不過逃不了的是政府管冶能量的消退。這裡不用「威信」這個詞，皆因已不存在了。"},{"pid":"673665e799f2d370ab2276121a92c71e60e0dece","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"呢篇文痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔唔係唔推下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093c50033b7be4d4f7ae8bb274b6bafcc10f384c","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dbce7439226e02e95f5ae2509884c3fc2e0e2d","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dd8755753aa1ba0071eb52a1c52babde174582","tid":1251469,"uid":260029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"曲直難分"},{"pid":"4b882ea0f2bf736243aace71e292cc41837159df","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68bc855678e066f457938f1b5535f75040c4e31","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a9e7d757a8df8ba382f7c470d186ee7fd6578a","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a27ed42fd6d0f538eda850053572fc60f92cb03","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a64d34e947a1f5c1ccf0efd4c858276235a6874","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538ef8bd70f503cc46e40bdda5f09fe975b01ab4","tid":1251469,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p